body_html:
@crimsontrigger
For further discussion, feel free to create another issue at AIY's github
https://github.com/google/aiyprojects-raspbian

If I understand your training correctly, you are training a faster_rccn_resnet model? Such model structure is not supported because of limited hardware resources on VisionKit.

Please see the section
https://aiyprojects.withgoogle.com/vision/#makers-guide--tensorflow-model-compiler
How to train and deploy a customized object detection model trained with TF’s object detection API?
